The function 
\emph on
Rd2roxygen()
\emph default
 can take a path of a source package, parse all the Rd files under the 
\family typewriter
man
\family default
 directory, and write the roxygen comments right above the source code of
 the functions under the 
\family typewriter
R
\family default
 directory.
\end_layout

